---
title: Piri Piri Chicken with Sweet Potatoes and Jalapeno Salsa
description: A Portuguese dish with its roots in Angola and Mozambique, dinner tonight brings the spice, sweetness and freshness of Piri Piri chicken to your table alongside a tasty jalapeno salsa!
